  "cooked": "<p>Here are updated reconstruction stats:</p>\n<p>I updated the <a href=\"https://public.peer.observer\">peer.observer</a> node <code>bob</code> to a recent <code>master</code> that includes <a href=\"https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/33106\" class=\"inline-onebox\">policy: lower the default blockmintxfee, incrementalrelayfee, minrelaytxfee by glozow \u00b7 Pull Request #33106 \u00b7 bitcoin/bitcoin \u00b7 GitHub</a>  on 2025-08-22. It didn\u2019t have existing sub-1 sat/vbyte transactions in it\u2019s mempool and thus took a few days before the reconstruction rate improved. Besides the bad reconstruction performance on 2025-09-06, 2025-09-07, and 2025-09-08, it performed significantly better.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/0/009ca9f430a11a4093fd8d1678d3cef57748d44b.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/009ca9f430a11a4093fd8d1678d3cef57748d44b\" title=\"Compact block reconstructions without requested transactions per day (higher is better). Data between 2025-07-01 and 2025-09-13.\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/009ca9f430a11a4093fd8d1678d3cef57748d44b_2_366x500.png\" alt=\"Compact block reconstructions without requested transactions per day (higher is better). Data between 2025-07-01 and 2025-09-13.\" data-base62-sha1=\"5pElKA9KEqc2kka2iTkHqlROXh\" width=\"366\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/009ca9f430a11a4093fd8d1678d3cef57748d44b_2_366x500.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/009ca9f430a11a4093fd8d1678d3cef57748d44b_2_549x750.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/009ca9f430a11a4093fd8d1678d3cef57748d44b_2_732x1000.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"EFCF95\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Compact block reconstructions without requested transactions per day (higher is better). Data between 2025-07-01 and 2025-09-13.</span><span class=\"informations\">983\u00d71341 254 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Similarly, a clear improvement in the average size of requested transactions can be seen for <code>bob</code>.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/8/8bc0dead2134d604ce7759af79f0b1d4630288e1.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/8bc0dead2134d604ce7759af79f0b1d4630288e1\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/8/8bc0dead2134d604ce7759af79f0b1d4630288e1_2_366x500.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"jWjAAkmdZ1QzAwegzagLENbtkml\" width=\"366\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/8/8bc0dead2134d604ce7759af79f0b1d4630288e1_2_366x500.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/8/8bc0dead2134d604ce7759af79f0b1d4630288e1_2_549x750.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/8/8bc0dead2134d604ce7759af79f0b1d4630288e1_2_732x1000.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"C7C68C\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">983\u00d71342 272 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
